%BB%93-Nam-m%E1%BA%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A7-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-UoNDKG9tHNLgUor6X9gSOA">Mộ thu tương quy Tần lưu biệt Hồ Nam mạc phủ thân hữu - 暮秋將歸秦留別湖南幕府親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%ADch-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-S%C3%A1n/Nam-H%E1%BA%A3i-t%E1%BB%AB-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-agv91UQ4lF8iHoLrEAlBhw">Nam Hải từ vịnh kỳ 1 - 南海祠詠其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%ADch-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-S%C3%A1n/author-raZnRizzmxsn-rfcNRwVcQ">Thích Đại Sán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Ki%C3%AAn-Ng%C3%B4/Ph%C3%BAng-s%C6%A1n-v%C3%A2n/poem-cpOLlJCfMCpGMzEuGFcqhQ">Phúng sơn vân - 諷山雲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi-Ki%C3%AAn-Ng%C3%B4/author-qmxkUt-i7s_YdIHj1-szkw">Thi Kiên Ngô</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-T%E1%BB%B1-Thanh/V%C5%A9/poem-7QVN-Hrhba-4FVMTfHVnqA">Vũ - 雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-T%E1%BB%B1-Thanh/author-wQICzKRVau8PqmJ28C9K6g">Cao Tự Thanh</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
